parser.grammar

Class Java8CommentSupportedBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.grammar.Java8CommentSupportedBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, Java8CommentSupportedListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RewriteFileVisitor, SimpleVisitor

    public class Java8CommentSupportedBaseListener
extends Object
implements Java8CommentSupportedListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of Java8CommentSupportedListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
